thumb.title: Mary Eleanor Photography
thumb.description: Mary Eleanor is a lifestyle, Virginia Beach Family Photographer, offering in-home & on-location sessions for young family's who want timeless, light & bright portraits.My purpose is to capture some of Motherhood's fleeting moments and make your life feel just a touch more beautiful in the chaos. From getting to know you, choosing the perfect location, styling your family, making sure you, Mama, feel beautiful, to getting your portraits printed and in your hands, I take care of all the beautiful details!Mary Eleanor PhotographyVirginia Beach, Virginia757-241-4400https://maryeleanorphotography.com/
